@startuml
skinparam monochrome true
actor User
boundary App
control SearchEngine
control RouteCalculator
entity Map

User -> App: type destination query
App -> SearchEngine: search(query)
SearchEngine --> App: destinations[]
User -> App: select destination
App -> RouteCalculator: computeRoute(Map, origin=GPS, dest, prefs)
RouteCalculator --> App: Path (points + instructions)
App --> User: show route + start navigation
@enduml
